results.title: Out of the Mouth of Babes
results.description:
Out of the Mouth of Babes

Picture it:  The year - mid 1980’s  Location:  Inside a popular department store in Awesome City, Texas.

As my young daughter and I walked into the store...she quickly inquires, “Mom, what are we going to buy here?”

“I need to find a couple of new bras” I replied.

“Ok” she said.

As I deligently searched thru numerous racks and shelves for the right bra style and size, my daughter asked me,

“Mom, how do you know what size to get?”

“Oh...ok...well...bras are measured by “Cups” from A thru D.  A is the smaller and D is the largest size.

My kid stepped back...looks at me and calmly states: 

“Mom, you don't need a “Cup”...you need “Jugs.”

I smiled at her and said, “Yes, you're probably right.”

I took her hand and said, “Come on sweetie...let's go to the pretzel store and get you your favorite snack.”

Trying extremely hard to contain myself from bursting into laughter as well as tears...her honest and truthful observation of my physical size made me realize it was definitely time to start a diet and exercise regime. 

(this gives a different meaning to "My Cup Runnith Over"...no?)

Esther Monsalve
The Angel Shop

Please note:  the items pictured (launch-time flower arrangements still in progress) are Not for sale in this listing...only one of the many fun times shopping experiences many years ago.  Thank you.

So...we do extra stuff to pay the bills like Etsy and a petting zoo (we have about 75 animals...and we like to take some to events on the weekends).  We are also Beachbody coaches.

We are parents AND foster parents, too! In our "spare" time, we work with children from trauma and those who are aging out of foster care without families.  Our non-profit, San Gabriel Springs, helps former foster youth as they navigate adulthood with no help, no role models, and no advice.  We have no paid employees and help around four (on average) young adults monthly with things like a new tire, electricity deposits, vet bills, college text books, new laptops or chromebooks, oil changes, and more. 

Thank you for checking out my shop!  If you can't purchase at this time, maybe you can share or favorite? It helps get the word out!

results.title: Primitive Decor, Live Laugh Love, Stars, Berries, Country Primitive, Art Print, Wall Hanging, Handmade, 8X8, Custom Wood Frame, Made in USA
results.description:
" Live Laugh Love " in a primitive design that measures only 8 X 8 in the handmade wood frame and will fit nicely where space is limited or fill in a small area to complete a decor.  This print has been adhered to a hard backboard and has a protective coating applied before being attached to a handmade wood frame that has been painted black. It has a hanger attached on the back for easy wall hanging or it could sit on a mantle piece or shelf. Made in the USA.

 All of the country and primitive prints that we finish are published work from various country artists such as Billy Jacobs, John Rossini, Ed Wargo, Lori Dieter, Robin-Lee Vieira, Tanya Crawford, Mary Ann June, Linda Spivey, Kim Norlien, Jim Hansel and others. The prints are adhered to a hard backboard and then a protective coating is applied to insure a long carefree life that adds a unique appearance which resembles a canvas original.

The handmade frames are cut from custom millwork which is of the highest quality material. The finished work can be displayed in any décor and enhances every type of style from formal and fancy to country and farmhouse. Because of the nature of real wood frames, each one is unique and a one-of-a-kind handmade piece. All are similar in appearance and match in size and style that compliment each other in paired or group settings. The black painted satin finish can also be custom ordered with a sanded primitive edge or also in other rustic colors. Custom orders are welcome, please message with requests.

The satisfaction and happiness of the customer are the two most important parts that go into each and every piece from Boggy Creek Primitives. I inspect every single piece before it is sent and if for any reason it is not 100% as you intended , then please contact me and I will make sure and do everything that I can so that you will be completely happy with your purchase.

Please visit our Etsy Shop for many more primitive and country framed prints and home decor. :
